'''2020年緬甸翡翠礦區塌方事故'''發生於2020年7月2日，當天在[[缅甸|缅甸]][[克钦邦|克钦邦]][[帕敢|帕敢]]翡翠礦區發生山體滑坡，導致至少有168人丧生。<ref name="BBC0702">{{Cite news|title=Myanmar jade mine landslide kills 120|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53260834|publisher=BBC|date=2020-07-02|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703025311/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53260834|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN0702">{{Cite news|title=Jade mine landslide kills at least 100 in Myanmar, with more people still missing|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/07/02/asia/myanmar-jade-mine-landslide-intl-hnk/index.html|publisher=CNN|date=2020-07-02|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703033155/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/07/02/asia/myanmar-jade-mine-landslide-intl-hnk/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==
[[缅甸|缅甸]]是[[玉|玉]]的最大開採国，該國[[克钦邦|克钦邦]][[帕敢|帕敢]]擁有全球最大的玉礦。全球90%以上玉石来自缅甸<ref>{{Cite web|title=翡翠喋血：缅甸玉石矿区发生严重矿难|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%BF%A1%E7%BF%A0%E5%96%8B%E8%A1%80%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%E7%8E%89%E7%9F%B3%E7%9F%BF%E5%8C%BA%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D%E7%9F%BF%E9%9A%BE/a-54025197|accessdate=|author=德國之聲|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703085247/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%BF%A1%E7%BF%A0%E5%96%8B%E8%A1%80%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%E7%8E%89%E7%9F%B3%E7%9F%BF%E5%8C%BA%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D%E7%9F%BF%E9%9A%BE/a-54025197|dead-url=no}}</ref>。緬甸每年的玉贸易额达300亿美元，但是其采矿场所经常发生事故。<ref name="BBC0702" />

2020年7月1日，[[缅甸|缅甸]][[克钦邦|克钦邦]][[帕敢|帕敢]]出現暴雨，緬甸当局发出警告，禁止在暴雨時采矿。但是这个警告被许多矿工所忽視。<ref name="BBC0702" />

2020年7月2日06:30，<ref name="CGTN0702">{{Cite news|title=Myanmar jade mine accident: 125 killed, some 200 trapped|url=https://news.cgtn.com/news/2020-07-02/33-killed-200-trapped-in-a-jade-mine-accident-in-Myanmar--RNjgRLWrn2/index.html|agency=CGTN|date=2020-07-02|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703033152/https://news.cgtn.com/news/2020-07-02/33-killed-200-trapped-in-a-jade-mine-accident-in-Myanmar--RNjgRLWrn2/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>暴雨引发了[[尾矿|尾礦]]的倒塌，塌下的泥石将那些在礦區採礦的人掩埋。<ref name="Reuters0702">{{Cite news|title=At least 113 killed as Myanmar jade mine collapse buries workers|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-myanmar-mine/at-least-113-killed-as-myanmar-jade-mine-collapse-buries-workers-idUSKBN2430M0|publisher=Reuters|date=2020-07-02|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702121400/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-myanmar-mine/at-least-113-killed-as-myanmar-jade-mine-collapse-buries-workers-idUSKBN2430M0|dead-url=no}}</ref>事發後救援人員抵達現場，經過搜尋後發現168具尸體，另有54人受傷<ref>{{Cite web|title=緬甸翡翠礦場嚴重塌方 最少113人死亡|url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1809813/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%BF%A1%E7%BF%A0%E7%A4%A6%E5%A0%B4%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%A1%8C%E6%96%B9-%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91113%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1|accessdate=|author=頭條日報|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813113232/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1809813/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%BF%A1%E7%BF%A0%E7%A4%A6%E5%A0%B4%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%A1%8C%E6%96%B9-%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91113%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

